data.description: Welcome to this spacious townhome conveniently located near Downtown Duluth, offering easy access to shopping, restaurants, and entertainment. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms, this residence spans three levels of comfortable living space. The main level features an inviting eat-in kitchen with quartz countertops, grey subway tile backsplash, and stainless appliances. Each bedroom comes with its own private bathroom, ensuring personal comfort and convenience. The large family room is accentuated by a cozy fireplace, ideal for relaxation or gatherings. Step outside to the fenced backyard, where the deck awaits for enjoyable outdoor entertaining. This townhome is part of a vibrant community offering amenities such as a neighborhood pool, a dog park, and a nature path for outdoor enthusiasts. Adjacent to the community lies WP Jones Park, providing additional recreational options including tennis courts. Experience the best of suburban living combined with urban conveniences in this desirable townhome. Don't miss out on this opportunity to call it home!
